</a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="flex flex-col justify-center bg-gray-50 py-24 sm:py-32 dark:bg-gray-900"><div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-8"><h2 class="mb-16 flex max-w-3xl flex-col text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl dark:text-white">Crypto buyers are already spending<span class="font-normal text-primary-400 dark:text-primary-200">Make sure they&#x27;re spending on you</span></h2><div class="flex flex-col gap-6"><div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-linear-to-br from-primary-100 to-white to-50% p-8 dark:from-gray-950 dark:to-gray-900" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 dark:hidden" style="background:radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 50% -20%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary-200) 50%, transparent), transparent)"></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 hidden dark:block" style="background:radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 50% -20%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-gray-950) 50%, transparent), transparent)"></div><span class="relative mb-6 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-primary-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-primary-700 ring-1 ring-primary-300 dark:bg-primary-900/40 dark:text-primary-300 dark:ring-primary-500/30">Numbers</span><div class="relative grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6"><div class="flex flex-col" style="opacity:0"><p class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 tabular-nums sm:text-4xl dark:text-white">0<span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400"></span></p><p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Operating since</p></div><div class="flex flex-col" style="opacity:0"><p class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 tabular-nums sm:text-4xl dark:text-white">0<span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">+</span></p><p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Countries</p></div><div class="flex flex-col" style="opacity:0"><p class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 tabular-nums sm:text-4xl dark:text-white">0<span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">+</span></p><p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Gift card brands</p></div><div class="flex flex-col" style="opacity:0"><p class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 tabular-nums sm:text-4xl dark:text-white">~<!-- -->0<span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">%</span></p><p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Orders to emerging markets</p></div><div class="flex flex-col" style="opacity:0"><p class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 tabular-nums sm:text-4xl dark:text-white">96.6<span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">%</span></p><p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Delivered &lt; 10s</p></div><div class="flex flex-col" style="opacity:0"><p class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 tabular-nums sm:text-4xl dark:text-white">Zero</p><p class="mt-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Zero chargebacks</p></div></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2"><div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-900 dark:ring-white/10" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)"><span class="mb-5 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-primary-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-primary-700 ring-1 ring-primary-200/60 dark:bg-primary-900/40 dark:text-primary-300 dark:ring-primary-500/30">Fees</span><h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">No listing fees.</h3><p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">You only pay when you earn. Revenue share on redemption only, no upfront cost, no platform minimums.</p><div class="mt-6"><div class="flex items-center justify-between border-t border-gray-100 py-3 first:border-t-0 dark:border-gray-800"><span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Listing fee</span><span class="text-base font-semibold tabular-nums text-emerald-500 dark:text-emerald-400">€0</span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between border-t border-gray-100 py-3 first:border-t-0 dark:border-gray-800"><span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Setup cost</span><span class="text-base font-semibold tabular-nums text-emerald-500 dark:text-emerald-400">€0</span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between border-t border-gray-100 py-3 first:border-t-0 dark:border-gray-800"><span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Revenue share</span><span class="text-base font-semibold tabular-nums text-gray-900 dark:text-white">On redemption</span></div></div></div><div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-linear-to-tl from-primary-100 to-50% p-8 dark:from-gray-950 dark:to-gray-900" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 dark:hidden" style="background:radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 100% 100%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-primary-200) 30%, transparent), transparent)"></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 hidden dark:block" style="background:radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 100% 100%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-gray-950) 30%, transparent), transparent)"></div><span class="relative mb-5 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-primary-50 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-primary-700 ring-1 ring-primary-200/60 dark:bg-primary-900/40 dark:text-primary-300 dark:ring-primary-500/30">Control</span><h3 class="relative text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Every aspect of your listing.</h3><p class="relative mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">A complete self-service portal. Set markets, pricing, timing, brand assets and inventory thresholds. Enable or disable SKUs in seconds.</p><div class="relative mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-3"><span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300 dark:ring-white/10">Markets</span><span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300 dark:ring-white/10">Pricing</span><span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300 dark:ring-white/10">Timing</span><span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300 dark:ring-white/10">Assets</span><span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300 dark:ring-white/10">Inventory</span><span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium whitespace-nowrap text-gray-700 ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300 dark:ring-white/10">Kill switch</span></div></div></div></div></div></section><section aria-label="How buyers pay with crypto" class="bg-linear-to-r dark:to-gray-900 py-24 sm:py-32 dark:from-gray-950 from-primary-100 to-white"><div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6"><h2 class="mb-12 flex max-w-3xl flex-col text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl dark:text-white">How buyers pay with crypto<span class="font-normal text-primary-400 dark:text-primary-200">Three steps to your code</span></h2></div><div class="no-scrollbar flex gap-6 overflow-x-auto px-4 lg:mx-auto lg:grid lg:w-full lg:max-w-6xl lg:grid-cols-3 lg:px-6"><div class="w-72 shrink-0 lg:w-auto"><div class="relative aspect-6/7 w-full overflow-