g:grid-cols-4"><div class="relative p-8" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)"><span class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-4 -left-1 z-0 text-[7rem] leading-none font-black text-gray-300/50 dark:text-gray-800/80 tabular-nums select-none ">01</span><svg viewBox="0 0 200 100" class="relative z-10 h-32 w-full" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect x="10" y="30" width="55" height="40" rx="6" class="fill-primary-100 stroke-primary-400/60 dark:fill-primary-800 dark:stroke-primary-400/40" stroke-width="1.5"></rect><rect x="135" y="30" width="55" height="40" rx="6" class="fill-primary-100 stroke-primary-400/60 dark:fill-primary-800 dark:stroke-primary-400/40" stroke-width="1.5"></rect><line x1="65" y1="50" x2="135" y2="50" class="stroke-primary-400/50" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4"></line><circle cx="100" cy="50" fill="none" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1.5"></circle><circle cx="100" cy="50" fill="none" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1.5"></circle><circle cx="100" cy="50" fill="none" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1.5"></circle><circle cx="100" cy="50" r="3" class="fill-primary-400"></circle></svg><p class="mt-6 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Intro call</p><p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">30 min to align on catalogue, pricing, and integration path.</p></div><div class="relative p-8" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)"><span class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-4 -left-1 z-0 text-[7rem] leading-none font-black text-gray-300/50 dark:text-gray-800/80 tabular-nums select-none ">02</span><svg viewBox="0 0 200 100" class="relative z-10 h-32 w-full" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect x="60" y="10" width="80" height="80" rx="4" class="fill-primary-100 stroke-primary-400/50 dark:fill-primary-800 dark:stroke-primary-400/30" stroke-width="1.5"></rect><path d="M120 10 L140 30 L120 30 Z" class="fill-primary-200 dark:fill-primary-700"></path><line x1="72" y1="40" x2="128" y2="40" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-dasharray="56" stroke-dashoffset="56"></line><line x1="72" y1="52" x2="118" y2="52" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-dasharray="46" stroke-dashoffset="46"></line><line x1="72" y1="64" x2="105" y2="64" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-dasharray="33" stroke-dashoffset="33"></line><path d="M118 75 L124 81 L134 68" class="stroke-emerald-500 dark:stroke-emerald-400" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><p class="mt-6 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Contract and SKU upload</p><p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Sign the agreement, share your catalogue. We handle the rest.</p></div><div class="relative p-8" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)"><span class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-4 -left-1 z-0 text-[7rem] leading-none font-black text-gray-300/50 dark:text-gray-800/80 tabular-nums select-none ">03</span><svg viewBox="0 0 200 100" class="relative z-10 h-32 w-full" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect x="20" y="15" width="160" height="70" rx="6" class="fill-gray-200 stroke-primary-400/30 dark:fill-gray-950 dark:stroke-primary-400/20" stroke-width="1.5"></rect><rect x="20" y="15" width="160" height="18" rx="6" class="fill-primary-400 dark:fill-primary-800"></rect><circle cx="32" cy="24" r="3" class="fill-red-500"></circle><circle cx="42" cy="24" r="3" class="fill-amber-500"></circle><circle cx="52" cy="24" r="3" class="fill-green-500"></circle><rect x="30" y="52" width="140" height="8" rx="4" class="fill-primary-200 dark:fill-primary-700"></rect><rect x="30" y="52" height="8" rx="4" class="fill-primary-500 dark:fill-primary-400"></rect><path d="M82 68 L90 76 L110 56" class="stroke-emerald-400" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><p class="mt-6 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Test in staging</p><p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Validate end-to-end before anything goes live.</p></div><div class="relative p-8" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)"><span class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-4 -left-1 z-0 text-[7rem] leading-none font-black text-gray-300/50 dark:text-gray-800/80 tabular-nums select-none ">04</span><svg viewBox="0 0 200 100" class="relative z-10 h-32 w-full" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><line x1="100" y1="50" x2="30" y2="20" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"></line><line x1="100" y1="50" x2="170" y2="20" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"></line><line x1="100" y1="50" x2="40" y2="80" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"></line><line x1="100" y1="50" x2="160" y2="80" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"></line><line x1="100" y1="50" x2="100" y2="8" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"></line><circle cx="30" cy="20" r="5" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1.5"></circle><circle cx="170" cy="20" r="5" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1.5"></circle><circle cx="40" cy="80" r="5" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1.5"></circle><circle cx="160" cy="80" r="5" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1.5"></circle><circle cx="100" cy="8" r="5" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1.5"></circle><circle cx="100" cy="50" fill="none" class="stroke-primary-400" stroke-width="1.5"></circle><circle cx="100" cy="50" r="8" class="fill-primary-400"></circle></svg><p class="mt-6 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Live in production</p><p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Your products live across Cryptorefills and all partners.</p></div></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3"><div class="group relative flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 transition-colors hover:border-primary-400 dark:border-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-950 dark:hover:border-primary-500" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)"><p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-primary-600 uppercase dark:text-primary-400">Integration</p><p class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">API or managed stock</p><p class="mt-3 flex-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Full REST API for large-scale partners. No-API managed stock model for brands without engineering infrastructure. Both paths reach the same distribution network.</p><div class="mt-6 mb-2 flex flex-col gap-2"><div class="dark:bg-primary-950 flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-primary-50 px-4 py-3 ring-1 ring-primary-200 dark:bg-gray-950 dark:ring-primary-400/20"><span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 dark:bg-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400"><svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path></svg></span><div><p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">REST API</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500">For engineering teams</p></div></div><div class="dark:bg-primary-950 flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-primary-50 px-4 py-3 ring-1 ring-primary-200 dark:bg-gray-950 dark:ring-primary-400/20"><span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 dark:bg-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400"><svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path></svg></span><div><p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Managed stock</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500">No engineering needed</p></div></div></div><a class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-primary-600 transition-colors group-hover:text-primary-700 after:absolute after:inset-0 dark:text-primary-400 dark:group-hover:text-primary-300" href="/en/contact-partnerships">Talk to partnerships<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon" class="h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 10a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h10.638L10.23 5.29a.75.75 0 1 1 1.04-1.08l5.5 5.25a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.08l-5.5 5.25a.75.75 0 1 1-1.04-1.08l4.158-3.96H3.75A.75.75 0 0 1 3 10Z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></a></div><div class="group relative flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 dark:border-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-950" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)"><p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-primary-600 uppercase dark:text-primary-400">API docs</p><p class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Developer-first documentation</p><p class="mt-3 flex-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Full API reference, authentication guide, webhook documentation, and live sandbox. Get from zero to first order in hours, not weeks.</p><div class="mt-6 mb-2 rounded-xl bg-gray-100 p-4 ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-950 dark:ring-primary-400/20"><div class="mb-2 flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/70"></span><span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/70"></span><span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500/70"></span></div><pre class="overflow-x-auto text-xs leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"><code><span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">POST</span> <!-- -->/v1/orders<!-- -->
<span class="text-gray-500">Authorization:</span> Bearer<!-- --> <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">sk_live_...</span>
<!-- -->
<span class="text-gray-500">{</span>
<!-- --> <span class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">&quot;product_id&quot;</span><span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">: </span><span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">&quot;gc_amazon_us_25&quot;</span>
<span class="text-gray-500">}</span></code></pre></div></div><div style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)"><div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl group"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 aspect-square w-[150vmax] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 animate-[spin_4s_linear_infinite] bg-[conic-gradient(transparent_0deg,transparent_60deg,#001588_120deg,#0022E0_160deg,#768AF9_180deg,#0022E0_200deg,#001588_240deg,transparent_300deg)] motion-reduce:animate-none"></div><div class="absolute inset-px rounded-[calc(1rem-1px)] bg-white dark:bg-gray-950"></div><div class="relative"><div class="flex flex-col p-8"><div class="relative flex items-start justify-between"><p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-primary-600 uppercase dark:text-primary-400">AI agents</p><span class="rounded-full bg-primary-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-primary-700 ring-1 ring-primary-300 dark:bg-primary-500/20 dark:text-primary-300 dark:ring-primary-500/30">New</span></div><p class="relative mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Discoverable by every AI agent</p><p class="relative mt-3 flex-1 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Cryptorefills exposes MCP APIs and supports x402 micropayment headers. Your products become natively accessible to autonomous AI agents without human checkout steps.</p><div class="relative mt-6 mb-2 rounded-xl bg-gray-100 p-4 ring-1 ring-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-950 dark:ring-primary-400/20"><div class="space-y-2"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5 flex h-5 w-5 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-100 text-xs dark:bg-primary-700">🤖</span><p class="rounded-lg rounded-tl-none bg-primary-50 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-gray-700 ring-1 ring-primary-200 dark:bg-primary-800 dark:text-gray-300 dark:ring-primary-400/15">Find me a $25 Amazon gift card.</p></div><div class="flex items-start justify-end gap-2"><p class="rounded-lg rounded-tr-none bg-primary-100 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-primary-700 ring-1 ring-primary-200 dark:bg-primary-700 dark:text-primary-300 dark:ring-primary-400/20">Found it. Paying via x402...</p><span class="mt-0.5 flex h-5 w-5 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-100 text-xs text-primary-600 dark:bg-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400">✓</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-0.5 flex h-5 w-5 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-100 text-xs dark:bg-primary-700">🤖</span><p class="rounded-lg rounded-tl-none bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-emerald-700 ring-1 ring-emerald-200 dark:bg-primary-800 dark:text-emerald-400 dark:ring-primary-400/15">Code delivered. No human needed.</p></div></div></div><a class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600 transition-colors group-hover:text-primary-700 after:absolute after:inset-0 dark:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-primary-200" href="/en/ai-agents">Explore AI agents<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon" class="h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 10a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h10.638L10.23 5.29a.75.75 0 1 1 1.04-1.08l5.5 5.25a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.08l-5.5 5.25a.75.75 0 1 1-1.04-1.08l4.158-3.96H3.75A.75.75 0 0 1 3 10Z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="mt-16 border-t border-gray-200 pt-10 dark:border-gray-800"><p class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Driving consumer adoption of crypto in ecommerce since 2018</p><a class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-600 transition-colors hover:text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400 dark:hover:text-primary-300" href="/en/about">Our story<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" data-slot="icon" class="h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 10a.75.75 0 0 1 .75-.75h10.638L10.23 5.29a.75.75 0 1 1 1.04-1.08l5.5 5.25a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.08l-5.5 5.25a.75.75 0 1 1-1.04-1.08l4.158-3.96H3.75A.75.75 0 0 1 3 10Z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></a></div></div></section></div><section class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32 dark:bg-gray-900"><div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between lg:flex-row lg:space-x-5"><div class="flex flex-col lg:w-1/3 lg:pr-10"><h2 class="mb-7 flex flex-col text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl dark:text-white">Common questions from brands</h2></div><div class="flex w-full flex-col items-center text-gray-600 sm:rounded-2xl lg:w-2/3"><div class="w-full"><dl class=" "><div><div class="space-y-6 divide-y divide-black/10 dark:divide-white/10"><div class="w-full pb-6" data-headlessui-state=""><dt><button class="flex w-full cursor-pointer items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200" id="headlessui-disclosure-button-_R_jdinpfr79fivb_" type="button" aria-expanded="false" data-headlessui-state=""><span class="text-base font-semibold">What types of products can I sell on Cryptorefills?</span><span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6" aria-hidden="true" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg></span></button></dt><dd class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-in-out grid-rows-[0fr]"><div class="overflow-hidden"><ul class="mt-2 pr-12"><li class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"><span>Cryptorefills supports digital products including gift cards, gaming credits, eSIM, mobile top up, travel bookings and subscription services. If you sell a digital or redeemable product, there is likely a place for it on our platform.</span></li></ul></div></dd></div><div class="w-full pb-6" data-headlessui-state=""><dt><button class="flex w-full cursor-pointer items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200" id="headlessui-disclosure-button-_R_ldinpfr79fivb_" type="button" aria-expanded="false" data-headlessui-state=""><span class="text-base font-semibold">Do I need to integrate via API to list my products?</span><span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6" aria-hidden="true" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg></span></button></dt><dd class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-in-out grid-rows-[0fr]"><div class="overflow-hidden"><ul class="mt-2 pr-12"><li class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"><span>No. We offer both API-based integrations for large-scale partners and a managed stock model for mid-size brands that don't have API infrastructure. Our team handles the operational setup.</span></li></ul></div></dd></div><div class="w-full pb-6" data-headlessui-state=""><dt><button class="flex w-full cursor-pointer items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200" id="headlessui-disclosure-button-_R_ndinpfr79fivb_" type="button" aria-expanded="false" data-headlessui-state=""><span class="text-base font-semibold">How does Cryptorefills handle settlement and chargebacks?</span><span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6" aria-hidden="true" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg></span></button></dt><dd class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-in-out grid-rows-[0fr]"><div class="overflow-hidden"><ul class="mt-2 pr-12"><li class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"><span>You see live sales in your portal as they happen, and invoice us on your own schedule. Most brands run monthly. We pay the invoice same-day in EUR, T+1 in USD, GBP, CHF or MXN, faster on stablecoins or BTC. Crypto rails don't reverse, so there are no chargebacks, and consumer-side disputes are ours to handle.</span></li></ul></div></dd></div><div class="w-full pb-6" data-headlessui-state=""><dt><button class="flex w-full cursor-pointer items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200" id="headlessui-disclosure-button-_R_pdinpfr79fivb_" type="button" aria-expanded="false" data-headlessui-state=""><span class="text-base font-semibold">How does Cryptorefills distribute products beyond its own website?</span><span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6" aria-hidden="true" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg></span></button></dt><dd class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-in-out grid-rows-[0fr]"><div class="overflow-hidden"><ul class="mt-2 pr-12"><li class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"><span>Cryptorefills has distribution partnerships with major crypto exchanges and wallets including KuCoin, Bitget, Kraken, World and others. Products listed with us are surfaced across these platforms, extending reach beyond our direct user base, including in regions where card-based distribution is thin.</span></li></ul></div></dd></div><div class="w-full pb-6" data-headlessui-state=""><dt><button class="flex w-full cursor-pointer items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200" id="headlessui-disclosure-button-_R_rdinpfr79fivb_" type="button" aria-expanded="false" data-headlessui-state=""><span class="text-base font-semibold">What is B2A and how does it apply to my brand?</span><span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6" aria-hidden="true" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg></span></button></dt><dd class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-in-out grid-rows-[0fr]"><div class="overflow-hidden"><ul class="mt-2 pr-12"><li class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"><span>B2A (Business to Agent) is a new commercial channel where AI agents autonomously discover and purchase products on behalf of users. Cryptorefills supports MCP APIs and the x402 payment protocol, making listed products natively accessible to AI shopping agents, a rapidly growing segment.</span></li></ul></div></dd></div><div class="w-full pb-6" data-headlessui-state=""><dt><button class="flex w-full cursor-pointer items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200" id="headlessui-disclosure-button-_R_tdinpfr79fivb_" type="button" aria-expanded="false" data-headlessui-state=""><span class="text-base font-semibold">What currencies does Cryptorefills accept?</span><span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6" aria-hidden="true" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line></svg></span></button></dt><dd class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-in-out grid-rows-[0fr]"><div class="overflow-hidden"><ul class="mt-2 pr-12"><li class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"><span>We accept all major stablecoins including USDT and USDC, Bitcoin (including via Lightning Network for instant low-fee payments) and all other leading crypto. We are also the first ecommerce platform to accept stablecoin payments via alternative networks including Avalanche, Solana and Polygon.</span></li></ul></div></dd></div></div></div></dl></div></div></div></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div><footer id="page-footer" class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800" aria-labelledby="footer-heading"><h2 id="footer-heading" class="sr-only">Footer</h2><div class="mx-auto max-w-(--breakpoint-xl) px-3 pt-14 pb-8"><div class="xl:grid xl:grid-cols-3 xl:gap-6"><div><svg width="818" height="127" viewBox="0 0 818 127" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-auto text-primary-900 sm:h-8 dark:text-primary-50"><path d="M74.1875 53.4375C74.1875 46.8542 75.25 40.6875 77.375 34.9375C79.5 29.1458 82.5417 24.1042 86.5 19.8125C90.5417 15.4375 95.25 12.1042 100.625 9.8125C106 7.47917 111.854 6.3125 118.188 6.3125C121.146 6.3125 124.229 6.58333 127.438 7.125C130.688 7.66667 133.562 8.41667 136.062 9.375C139.146 10.5417 141.521 12.1042 143.188 14.0625C144.896 15.9792 145.75 18.1875 145.75 20.6875C145.75 22.2292 145.396 23.6667 144.688 25C143.979 26.2917 143.021 27.3125 141.812 28.0625C140.646 28.8542 139.312 29.25 137.812 29.25C136.604 29.25 134.688 28.7708 132.062 27.8125C128.729 26.5208 126.25 25.6875 124.625 25.3125C123 24.9375 120.854 24.75 118.188 24.75C114.396 24.75 110.979 25.4792 107.938 26.9375C104.896 28.3958 102.354 30.5 100.312 33.25C98.3125 35.875 96.7708 38.9583 95.6875 42.5C94.6458 46.0417 94.125 49.8125 94.125 53.8125C94.125 59.2292 95.0833 64.0833 97 68.375C98.9583 72.625 101.75 75.9792 105.375 78.4375C109.083 80.8958 113.354 82.125 118.188 82.125C121.146 82.125 123.646 81.8125 125.688 81.1875C127.729 80.5625 130 79.6667 132.5 78.5C134.958 77.3333 136.979